[Although ProMED-mail does not normally post pieces about dengue fever in
regions of the world in which the disease is endemic, it does so when there
are outbreaks of dengue hemorrhagic fever. In this situation, the
declaration by El Salvador's president that there is a national emergency
due to dengue fever and the rising number of deaths certainly merits
posting as does the alert for Honduras.
We would be interested to learn further details of the situations in El
Salvador and Honduras. -Man. Ed. DS
